Problem 1l

ar_model = lm(price ~ lag1 + lag2 + lag3 + lag4 + lag5, data = gme)
gme$res[6:314] = residuals(ar_model)
plot.ts(gme$res, ylab = "Residual")
abline(a = 0, b = 0)
